{"tid":2222481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊入黎屌9留任泛民","createTime":"2020-09-29T06:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T08:04:14.000Z","uid":66278,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b90f8e2e257d4d5d952b3e4e7ee27c84ea484e3e","tid":2222481,"uid":66278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"所有決定留任嘅泛民議員，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>你地嘅醜惡我地所有香港人都看在眼𥚃！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>我地真係好嬲你地！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地跟本從一開始就已經有<span class=\"red\">既定立場</span>要留任，但仲要扮哂民主做民調。<br />\n<br />\n民調都做左幾次，今次格硬做到岩自己心水就公佈出黎支持自己？<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>你地同嗰班仆街高官又有乜嘢分別？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你地最可恥嘅就係你地跟本就無積極掙取過立即重啟立法會選舉！咁等同於反抗都唔反抗，乖乖聽中央話，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">咁我地仲點樣相信你地可以代表我地去掙取呀？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n依家我地有共同敵人，暫且不分化不追擊你地。<br />\n<br />\n但他朝一日我有選票，只要有今次選擇留任以外嘅人選，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>我都一定唔會再含淚投票俾你地！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n立此存照"},{"pid":"f3dfb9b703edef4b78a000386684c6568fbe9026","tid":2222481,"uid":66278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea8891c4cb54cb3faaf9bb2dd42227aa883f572","tid":2222481,"uid":66278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f